        "TileImage": "$($repository 22d36967-af1e-4329-9921-03b851e4018c).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Our client today is an employee at a skyscraper in Dubai. However, in recent years he has begun to notice racist, submissive and generally abusive behavior from his manager, Cindy Burns. The client wants revenge, but first he needs the money. So he plans to rob the company of just enough money to pay us, but first we still have to murder the bank teller, rob the &quot;Tablet&quot; from the &quot;Guest bedroom&quot; safe. Good luck 47. And as always... Have fun!",
